@page "/"

<PageTitle>TaskFlow – Personal Task Manager</PageTitle>

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Stay on top of everything.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            TaskFlow is a simple, personal task manager for students and young professionals.
            Create tasks, organize by category, and track what you've accomplished — all in one place.
        </p>
        <AuthorizeView>
            <Authorized>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Go to My Tasks</a>
            </Authorized>
            <NotAuthorized>
                <a href="/Account/Register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-2">Get Started</a>
                <a href="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">Log In</a>
            </NotAuthorized>
        </AuthorizeView>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="features">
    <h2 class="features-heading">Everything you need, nothing you don't.</h2>
    <div class="feature-cards">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">&#10003;</div>
            <h3>Create &amp; Manage Tasks</h3>
            <p>Add tasks with a title and optional description. Edit or delete them anytime, and mark them complete when you're done.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">&#9782;</div>
            <h3>Organize by Category</h3>
            <p>Assign each task to a category like <strong>School</strong>, <strong>Work</strong>, or <strong>Personal</strong> to keep things organized.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">&#128274;</div>
            <h3>Your Tasks, Only Yours</h3>
            <p>Each account is private. Log in securely and see only your own tasks — no shared lists, no clutter.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
